description: [``botocore``] This release adds support to send VPC Flow Logs to kinesis-data-firehose as new destination type
[``botocore``] EMR on EKS now allows running Spark SQL using the newly introduced Spark SQL Job Driver in the Start Job Run API
[``botocore``] Release dimension value filtering feature to allow customers to define dimension filters for including only a subset of their dataset to be used by LookoutMetrics.
[``botocore``] This change exposes API settings which allow Dolby Atmos and Dolby Vision to be used when running a channel using Elemental Media Live
[``botocore``] Amazon Route 53 now supports the Middle East (UAE) Region (me-central-1) for latency records, geoproximity records, and private DNS for Amazon VPCs in that region.
[``botocore``] This release adds Mode to AutoMLJobConfig.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for Systems Manager State Manager Association tagging.
